Arder is back with part 2 of our warehouse series at ESC.  For the occasion we have the pleasure of inviting one of the most influential names in the techno world. His productions have no doubt shaped the sound of recent techno. Formally known as Audio Injection, Truncate focuses on the deeper, raw side of techno. His Truncate releases have gained critical acclaim from world class underground talent such as Modeselektor, Ben Klock, Marcel Dettmann, Chris Liebing, Speedy J, DVS1, Luke Slater, Ben Sims, Josh Wink, Eats Everything, Joris Voorn, and many more.

The Nightmare Before Christmas: Toy Drive & Fundraiser

Nightmare Before Christmas @ Francesco’s  Celebrate the holidays with a twist at Francesco’s Discoteca! Immerse yourself in the enchanting Nightmare Before Christmas theme, where Jack Skellington and friends come alive in a festive frenzy. Dance under the twinkling lights, marvel at the hauntingly beautiful decor, enjoy our signature cocktails and join us in spreading Christmas cheer with a charitable touch.  Event Highlights:  • Festive Atmosphere: Experience the magic of the season with our themed wonderland.  • Toy Drive: Share the gift of joy by bringing a new, unwrapped toy for our Toy Drive. Help us make Christmas extra special for children in need.  • Charitable Giving: This holiday, every ticket you purchase goes to the Make-A-Wish Quebec Foundation. Join us in making dreams come true for children facing critical illnesses.  Get your tickets now and be part of a fun celebration with a heartwarming twist

ROMAN’S DANCE FLOOR HAS AN ETHOS: BEND THE EAR WITH LIFE-GIVING BODY-FREQUENCY AND LEAVE THE CLUB ALTERED. THEIR SIGNATURE BLENDS OF LATIN CLUB, BREAKS, BALTIMORE CLUB, FOOTWORK, MASH-UPS AND EUPHORIC DANCE TECHNO DO JUST THAT. THEY PRODUCE FIERCE DECONSTRUCTED POST-CLUB TRACKS UNDER SKULPTOR AND RUN FOKUS GLOBAL EVENTS IN NYC - A MONTHLY KNOWN FOR CLOSE DANCING, HIGH-OCTANE ENERGY, GLOBAL BEATS, AND HEADY ROMANCE ON THE DANCEFLOOR. EARS THAT LOVE ARCA, DJ PYTHON, FLORENTINO, LAUREL HALO, ABADIR, AND FRACTAL FANTASY CAN HEAR ROMAN'S DEDICATION NOT ONLY AS FOKUS GLOBAL LABEL MAMA BUT AS A SOUND DESIGNER, PRODUCER, AND MULTIDISCIPLINARY CREATIVE TECHNOLOGIST. RIGHT NOW ROMAN HAS EARNED A SPACE ON NYC DANCEFLOORS AND IS QUICKLY GAINING AN INTERNATIONAL AUDIENCE IN EUROPE AND LATIN AMERICA.

Block Party Bonne Famille x Club Sagacité

The Bonne Famille and Club Sagacité collectives are proud to invite you to their final Block Party of the summer, in partnership with the Corridor Culturel organization, on Saturday, October 7th at the Corridor Festival. From 2:00 PM to 10:30 PM , immerse yourself in a day of exceptional musical, visual, and culinary experiences.  Furthermore, don't miss the opportunity to attend a DJ class with artist San Farafina, which will take place on-site from 2:00 PM to 3:30 PM.   Everything will be happening at Hangar 1825, with its backyard and indoor space capable of accommodating over 400 people.   Join us for a festive, dance-filled, and inclusive atmosphere where everyone is welcome. Act fast and reserve your ticket now.
